@page "/services"

<PageOutlet Url="services"
            Title="Services"
            Description="different services available in the bit platform's software development as a service" />

<div class="services-bg">
    <section class="page-sec services">
        <div class="services-title">Our Services</div>
        @* <div class="services-bread">Home &rarr; Services</div> *@
    </section>
    <section class="page-sec outsource-your-concerns">
        <div class="sec-body">
            <div class="sec-title">Outsource your Concerns<br />in Software Development Services</div>
            <div class="sec-desc">
                With focus on cost-efficiency and agile development, we can help you scale up your business, achieve your goals and integrate 
                e-commerce as soon as possible. bit foundation works round the clock and tirelessly to make sure we deliver more than you expect.
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<section class="page-sec outsourcing">
    <div class="sec-title">Full-service business process outsourcing</div>
    <div class="sec-desc">
        At bit, we empower businesses to reach their full potential by providing cutting-edge services that streamline operations 
        and allow them to focus on their core competencies.
    </div>
    <div class="sec-content">
        <div class="steps-bg-1"></div>
        <div class="steps-container">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-title">Product Design</div>
                <div class="step-desc">
                    Your idea deserves an impeccable future, so do you. The art of product design is not just in creating a beautifully 
                    crafted product but to truly understand your user needs and empathize with them. But what makes this idea even more 
                    brilliant is to execute it cost-effectively and in the shortest time possible.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-title">Dedicated Team of Experts</div>
                <div class="step-desc">
                    Let us boom your business through the power of people. We are more than lucky to have only the best of the 
                    best by our side. Whether you're launching a startup or working on further growth of your scaleup, we make 
                    sure the right experts are assigned to your specific needs.
                    <br />
                    <a href="/process#art">see all roles in a team</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step" id="solutions">
                <div class="step-title">Modern Solutions</div>
                <div class="step-desc">
                    Utilizing cutting-edge technologies throughout your business growth process is an absolute must. With the right 
                    technologies that fit your business needs, your business will be swift and efficient in ways never before possible.
                </div>
                <div class="solutions-container">
                    <ProcessAccordion Title="Web development">
                        <div>
                            Your business is unique and must be run on a unique platform. We offer custom web development for your business. 
                            We make sure that your website is responsive and works perfectly and beautifully on tablet, desktop and smartphone 
                            browsers. Our team specializes in making great custom-made websites.
                        </div>
                        <div class="tags">
                            <div class="tag">React</div>
                            <div class="tag">Vue.js</div>
                            <div class="tag">Angular</div>
                            <div class="tag">Blazor</div>
                            <div class="tag">PHP</div>
                            <div class="tag">ASP.NET</div>
                        </div>
                    </ProcessAccordion>
                    <ProcessAccordion Title="Mobile development">
                        <div>
                            Unlock the full potential of your business with our world-class mobile development services. 
                            Our team of experts will work with you to design, develop, and deliver custom mobile solutions 
                            that drive engagement and increase revenue.
                        </div>
